          "docs": "Gets a list of all alerts the application has access too."
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Get Alert Runs",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.lexmachina.com/alerts/runs/:alert_id",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "alert_id",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "token": "{{bearerToken}}"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Gets a list of all runs an alert has new data for.\n\n- **alert_id**: the id of the alert\n\nEach run represents a new set of relevant items that have been found by the alert on a given day."
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Get Alert Run Results",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.lexmachina.com/alerts/runs/:alert_id/:date",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "alert_id",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path"
              },
              {
                "name": "date",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "token": "{{bearerToken}}"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Gets a list of all new items for a given alert run.\n\n- **alert_id**: the id of the alert\n- **date**: the date of the run\n\nData returned for an alert run will vary in format based on context, only the ids and urls for the relevant data will included."
        }
      ]
    },
